Q_DESC: Write a java program to check whether two given strings are anagram or not. Two strings are said to be anagram if they contain same set of characters but in different order. For example, Mother In Law and Hitler Woman are anagrams.
TESTCASE_1:
keEp
peeK
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
keEp and peeK are anagrams
TESTCASE_2:
keEp
peak
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
keEp and peak are not anagrams
TESTCASE_3:
Mother In Law
Hitler Woman
###---###SEPERATOR---###---
Mother In Law and Hitler Woman are anagrams
